metrictools v0.8.0 beta;

  * Renamed the project from "FnordMetric" to metrictools

  * Added the metrictl command line utility and broke functionalty up into a
    number of commands

  * Added the SQLite backend

  * Added the configuration file

  * Added units of measurement

  * Added the label_set stanza

  * Added the collect_http and collect_proc facilities

  * Added the gauge and monotonic metric types

  * Added the borgmon/prometheus input format parser

